title: Utada Hikaru - Utada United (2006) [FLAC]
description:
I ripped this audio from the 2006 'Utada United' DVD into FLAC using DVD Audio Extractor. Initially I just did this for myself because I was a huge fan of this show but after recently going thru my audio collection I figured other Utada fans might be interested in having this so I decided to upload it. Enjoy!
